msgid "Bland-Altman Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Bland-Altman"

msgid ""
"Bland-Altman plots of the mean vs. difference for each variable pair, with "
"mean difference and limits of agreement."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Scatter plot of mean vs. difference of the two measurements. The middle "
"dashed line is the mean difference (bias); the outer dashed lines are the "
"limits of agreement (±1.96 SD)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Please provide another variable"
msgstr "Silakan sediakan variabel lain"

msgid "Plotting not possible: %s"
msgstr "Pembuatan plot tidak memungkinkan: %s"

msgid "Bland-Altman Tables"
msgstr "Tabel Bland-Altman"

msgid ""
"Summary statistics for each pair: bias (mean difference), limits of "
"agreement, and optional confidence intervals."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Mean difference (bias), lower and upper limits of agreement for this pair. "
"If confidence intervals are requested, uncertainty bounds for each limit are "
"also shown."
msgstr ""

msgid "Bias & Limits"
msgstr "Bias & Batas"

msgid "Point Value"
msgstr "Nilai Titik"

msgid "Mean difference - 1.96 SD"
msgstr "Perbedaan rerata - 1.96 SD"

msgid "Mean difference + 1.96 SD"
msgstr "Perbedaan rerata + 1.96 SD"

msgid "Mean difference"
msgstr "Perbedaan rerata"

msgid "Lower %s%% CI"
msgstr "%s%% CI bawah"

msgid "Upper %s%% CI"
msgstr "%s%% CI atas"

msgid "Calculations not possible: %s"
msgstr "Perhitungan tidak memungkinkan: %s"

msgid "Intraclass Correlation"
msgstr "Korelasi Intrakelas"

msgid ""
"Intraclass correlation coefficients (ICC) with optional confidence intervals "
"for assessing absolute agreement or consistency among raters."
msgstr ""

msgid "Type"
msgstr "Jenis"

msgid "Point Estimate"
msgstr "Estimasi Titik"

msgid ""
"%1$s subjects and %2$s raters/measurements. ICC type as referenced by Shrout "
"& Fleiss (1979)."
msgstr ""
"%1$s subjek dan %2$s penilai/pengukuran. Jenis ICC direferensikan oleh "
"Shrout & Fleiss (1979)."

msgid "Please select at least 2 columns"
msgstr "Silakan pilih setidaknya 2 kolom"

#, fuzzy
msgid "Agreement Coefficient"
msgstr "Koefisien"

msgid ""
"Empty placeholder table shown while no agreement coefficient is selected; "
"check a coefficient to obtain results."
msgstr ""

msgid "Coefficient"
msgstr "Koefisien"

msgid "Estimate"
msgstr "Estimasi"

msgid "SE"
msgstr "SE"

msgid "Lower"
msgstr "Batas Bawah"

msgid "Upper"
msgstr "Batas Atas"

msgid "Check one of the coefficients to start the analysis."
msgstr ""

msgid "%s%% CI"
msgstr "%s%% CI"

msgid ""
"%s requires a common ordinal scale, but the declared category orders of the "
"raters are contradictory or do not determine a unique order. Ensure all "
"raters use the same ordered categories."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"With raters in rows, all subject/item columns must have the same measurement "
"type. The data mix categorical and continuous columns; change the column "
"types so they match."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Krippendorff's alpha requires at least 2 raters/measurements."
msgstr "Kappa Fleiss memerlukan setidaknya 2 penilai/pengukuran."

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha with an interval or ratio method requires numeric "
"ratings. Use the nominal or ordinal method, or recode the data."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha with the ratio method requires non-negative ratings."
msgstr ""

msgid "Krippendorff's alpha with the ordinal method"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha cannot be computed: the data contain infinite values."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha cannot be computed: no subject/item was rated by at "
"least 2 raters (no pairable observations)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha is not estimable: the pairable ratings do not vary."
msgstr ""

msgid "Cohen's kappa"
msgstr "Kappa Cohen"

msgid ""
"Cohen's kappa: chance-corrected agreement between exactly two raters. Ranges "
"from -1 (worse than chance) to 1 (perfect agreement)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Ratings"
msgstr "Peningkatan"

msgid "kappa"
msgstr "kappa"

msgid ""
"Cohen's kappa requires nominal or ordinal variables. Remove scale variables "
"or change their type."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Weighted Cohen's kappa requires ordinal variables. Remove nominal variables "
"or change their type."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Cohen's kappa requires at least 2 raters/measurements."
msgstr "Kappa Fleiss memerlukan setidaknya 2 penilai/pengukuran."

#, fuzzy
msgid "Weighted Cohen's kappa"
msgstr "Kappa Cohen"

msgid "fewer than 3 jointly rated subjects/items"
msgstr ""

msgid "the ratings do not vary"
msgstr ""

msgid "the coefficient is not estimable"
msgstr ""

msgid "Cohen's kappa could not be computed for any rater pair: %s."
msgstr ""

msgid "Some rater pairs could not be computed:"
msgstr ""

msgid ". They are excluded from the average kappa."
msgstr ""

msgid "Note:"
msgstr ""

msgid "%1$i subjects/items and %2$i raters/measurements."
msgstr "%1$i subjek/item dan %2$i penilai/pengukuran."

msgid "%1$s Based on pairwise complete cases."
msgstr "%1$s Berdasarkan kasus lengkap berpasangan."

msgid "n"
msgstr ""

msgid "Confidence intervals are asymptotic."
msgstr "Interval kepercayaan adalah asimptotik."

msgid ""
"If there are only 2 levels, weighted kappa is equal to unweighted kappa."
msgstr ""
"Jika hanya ada2 tingkat, kappa berberat sama dengan kappa tidak berberat."

msgid "Cohen's kappa requires at least 3 subjects/items."
msgstr "Kappa Cohen memerlukan setidaknya 3 subjek/item."

msgid "Fleiss' kappa"
msgstr "Kappa Fleiss"

msgid ""
"Fleiss' kappa: generalization of Cohen's kappa for two or more raters "
"assigning subjects to nominal categories."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Fleiss' kappa requires nominal or ordinal variables. Remove scale variables "
"or change their type."
msgstr ""

msgid "Fleiss' kappa requires at least 2 raters/measurements."
msgstr "Kappa Fleiss memerlukan setidaknya 2 penilai/pengukuran."

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Fleiss' kappa requires at least 3 complete subjects/items (rows without "
"missing ratings). Check whether raters are in columns or rows."
msgstr ""
"Kappa Fleiss memerlukan setidaknya 3 subjek/item. Periksa apakah penilai "
"berada di kolom atau baris."

msgid ""
"Fleiss' kappa is not estimable: all ratings fall into a single category."
msgstr ""

msgid "%1$s Based on listwise complete cases."
msgstr "%1$s Berdasarkan kasus lengkap berdaftar."

msgid "Krippendorff's alpha"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Krippendorff's alpha: reliability coefficient applicable to any number of "
"raters, any scale level (nominal/ordinal/interval/ratio), and incomplete "
"data."
msgstr ""

msgid "Method"
msgstr "Metode"

msgid "Krippendorff's alpha is not estimable for these data."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"%1$i of %2$i bootstrap samples could not be computed and were excluded from "
"the CI."
msgstr ""

msgid "Kendall's W"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Kendall's coefficient of concordance W: measures agreement of rankings "
"across multiple raters. Ranges from 0 (no agreement) to 1 (perfect "
"concordance). Significance is assessed with the large-sample chi-square test "
"and the F test, which performs better for small samples."
msgstr ""

msgid "Chi-square test"
msgstr ""

msgid "F test"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Kendall's W requires ordinal or scale variables. Remove nominal variables."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Kendall's W requires at least 2 raters/measurements."
msgstr "Kappa Fleiss memerlukan setidaknya 2 penilai/pengukuran."

msgid ""
"Kendall's W requires at least 2 complete subjects/items (rows without "
"missing ratings)."
msgstr ""

msgid "Kendall's W cannot be computed: the data contain infinite values."
msgstr ""

msgid "Kendall's W is not estimable: the rankings do not vary."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Bootstrap CIs are only available with the tie correction enabled: resampling "
"with replacement introduces ties, which distort the uncorrected coefficient."
msgstr ""

#, fuzzy
msgid "Confidence intervals are based on bootstrap."
msgstr "Interval kepercayaan adalah asimptotik."

msgid "Chi-square test is valid for large samples only."
msgstr ""

msgid "The F test is undefined for perfect concordance (W = 1)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The F test is not available for this design: it requires n - 1 - 2/m > 0 (n "
"= subjects/items, m = raters)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Ties are present in the ratings, so the uncorrected coefficient may be "
"inaccurate. Consider enabling the tie correction."
msgstr ""

msgid "Warning:"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"For the Lord generalized method, the test could not be split in equally "
"sized parts with more than 1 item per part. Consider adding or removing "
"items."
msgstr ""
"Untuk metode tergeneralisasi Lord, pengujian tidak dapat dipisahkan dalam "
"bagian berukur secara sama dengan lebih dari 1 item per bagian. "
"Pertimbangkan menambahkan atau menghapus item."

msgid "Standard error of measurement results for the selected methods."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The Lord, Keats, and Lord generalized method are only available for binary "
"data."
msgstr ""
"Metode Lord, Keats, dan tergeneralisasi Lord hanya tersedia untuk data biner."

msgid "Standard Error of Measurement"
msgstr "Galat Standar dari Pengukuran"

msgid ""
"Conditional standard error of measurement (SEM) for each sum score using the "
"selected method(s). The unconditional SEM is also shown."
msgstr ""

msgid "Sum Score"
msgstr "Skor Jumlah"

msgid "Unconditional SEM"
msgstr "SEM Tidak Kondisional"

msgid "Counts"
msgstr "Cacah"

msgid "%1$s The unconditional SEM value equals %2$1.3f."
msgstr "%1$s Nilai SEM tidak kondisional sama dengan %2$1.3f."

msgid ""
"%1$s Estimating the %2$s method failed. If possible, you might try changing "
"the method's parameters."
msgstr ""
"%1$s Mengestimasi metode %2$s gagal. Jika memungkinkan, Anda mungkin mencoba "
"mengubah parameter metode."

msgid "Sum Score CI Table"
msgstr "Tabel CI Skor Jumlah"

msgid ""
"Confidence intervals for the true score at each sum score level, computed "
"from the conditional SEM."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Estimating the %s method failed. If possible, you might try changing the "
"method's parameters."
msgstr ""
"Mengestimasi metode %s gagal. Jika memungkinkan, Anda mungkin mencoba "
"mengubah parameter metode."

msgid "Histogram of Counts per Sum Score Group"
msgstr "Histogram dari Hitungan per Grup Skor Jumlah"

msgid "Distribution of participants across sum score groups."
msgstr ""

msgid "Point Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Titik"

msgid ""
"Conditional SEM plotted as a function of sum score for each selected method."
msgstr ""

msgid "SEM"
msgstr "SEM"

msgid "Combined Plot"
msgstr "Diagram Terkombinasi"

msgid ""
"Overlay of all selected methods' conditional SEM across the full range of "
"sum scores."
msgstr ""

msgid "Sum Score CI Plots"
msgstr "Diagram CI Skor Jumlah"

msgid ""
"True-score confidence interval plotted against sum score for each selected "
"method."
msgstr ""

msgid "True Score Estimate"
msgstr "Estimasi Skor Benar"

msgid "Split-half coefficient"
msgstr "Koefisien terpisah-setengah"

msgid "Item-rest correlation"
msgstr "Korelasi sisa-item"

msgid "Mean"
msgstr "Rata-rata"

msgid "Variance"
msgstr "Varians"

msgid "SD"
msgstr "SD"

msgid "%1$s Of the observations, %2$1.f complete cases were used."
msgstr "%1$s Dari observasi, %2$1.f kasus lengkap telah digunakan."

msgid "%s Of the observations, pairwise complete cases were used."
msgstr "%1$s Dari observasi, kasus lengkap berpasangan telah digunakan."

msgid ""
"Sampling the posterior covariance matrix for either one of [alpha, lambda2, "
"lambda6, glb] failed. Try changing to 'Exclude cases listwise' in 'Advanced "
"Options'"
msgstr ""
"Mensampelkan matriks kovarians posterior untuk baik satu dari [alfa, "
"lambda2, lambda6, glb] gagal. Coba mengubah ke 'Kecualikan kasus berdaftar' "
"di 'Opsi Lanjutan'"

msgid ""
"Sampling the posterior covariance matrix for either one of [alpha, lambda2, "
"lambda6, glb] failed."
msgstr ""
"Mensampelkan matriks kovarians posterior untuk baik satu dari [alfa, "
"lambda2, lambda6, glb] gagal."

msgid ""
"Sampling the posterior factor model for omega failed. Try changing to "
