msgid "Bayesian Scale Reliability Statistics"
msgstr "Statistik Keandalan Skala Bayes"

msgid ""
"Bayesian posterior estimates and credible intervals for all selected scale "
"reliability coefficients."
msgstr ""

msgid "Posterior %s"
msgstr "Posterior %s"

msgid "R-hat"
msgstr "R-hat"

msgid "ESS"
msgstr "ESS"

msgid "Bayesian Individual Item Reliability Statistics"
msgstr "Statistik Keandalan Item Individu Bayes"

msgid ""
"Bayesian item-level reliability: posterior estimates of the scale "
"coefficient if each item were dropped, and item-rest correlations."
msgstr ""

msgid "Item"
msgstr "Item"

msgid "%s (if item dropped)"
msgstr "%s (jika item dihapus)"

msgid ""
"%s Please enter at least 3 variables for the if item dropped statistics."
msgstr ""
"%s Silakan masukkan setidaknya 3 variabel untuk statistik jika item dihapus."

msgid ""
"The bounds you entered have been rearranged in increasing order to provide "
"meaningful results."
msgstr ""
"Batas yang Anda masukkan telah disusun ulang dalam pengurutan peningkatan "
"untuk menyediakan hasil berarti."

msgid ""
"Probability that Reliability Coefficient is Larger than %1$.2f and Smaller "
"than %2$.2f"
msgstr ""
"Probabilitas bahwa Koefisien Keandalan Lebih Besar dari %1$.2f dan Lebih "
"Kecil dari %2$.2f"

msgid ""
"Posterior and prior probability that each reliability coefficient falls "
"within the specified interval."
msgstr ""

msgid "Probability"
msgstr "Probabilitas"

msgid "Prior"
msgstr "Priori"

msgid "Posterior"
msgstr "Posterior"

msgid "Fit Measures for the Single-Factor Model"
msgstr "Pengukuran Penyesuaian untuk Model Satu Faktor"

msgid ""
"Bayesian fit indices for the single-factor model underlying McDonald's omega."
msgstr ""

msgid "%s lower bound"
msgstr "%s batas bawah"

msgid "%s upper bound"
msgstr "%s batas atas"

msgid ""
"'Relative to cutoff'-row denotes the probability that the B-RMSEA is smaller "
"than\n"
"                         the corresponding cutoff and the probabilities that "
"the B-CFI/TLI are larger than the\n"
"                         corresponding cutoff."
msgstr ""
"Baris-'Relatif dengan cutoff' menandakan probabilitas bahwa B-RMSEA lebih "
"kecil dari\n"
"                         cutoff sesuai dan probabilitas bahwa B-CFI/TLI "
"lebih besar dari\n"
"                         cutoff sesuai."

msgid "Standardized Loadings of the Single-Factor Model"
msgstr "Pemuatan Terstandardisasi dari Model Satu Faktor"

#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Posterior estimates of standardized factor loadings from the single-factor "
"model."
msgstr "Pemuatan Terstandardisasi dari Model Satu Faktor"

msgid "Standardized loading"
msgstr "Pemuatan Terstandardisasi"

msgid "Posterior Plots"
msgstr "Diagram Posterior"

msgid ""
"Posterior density plots for each selected reliability coefficient, with "
