msgstr "Nilai Eigen No."

msgid "Posterior Predictive Check Omega"
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Posterior predictive check: observed eigenvalues of the covariance matrix "
"compared against the model-implied posterior distribution to assess single-"
"factor model fit."
msgstr ""

msgid "Convergence Traceplot"
msgstr "Diagram lacak konvergensi"

msgid ""
"Traceplots of MCMC samples per chain over iterations to assess sampler "
"convergence and mixing."
msgstr ""

msgid "Iterations"
msgstr "Iterasi"

msgid "Average interitem correlation"
msgstr "Korelasi interitem rata-rata"

msgid "%1$s%2$s"
msgstr "%1$s%2$s"

msgid ""
"Omega calculation with CFA failed.\n"
"                                                    Try changing to PFA in "
"'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"Perhitungan omega dengan CFA gagal.\n"
"                                                    Coba mengubah ke PFA di "
"'Opsi Lanjutan'."

msgid ""
"Omega bootstrapped interval calculation with CFA failed.\n"
"                                                        Try changing to PFA "
"in 'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"Perhitungan interval terbootstrap omega dengan CFA gagal.\n"
"                                                        Coba mengubah ke PFA "
"di 'Opsi Lanjutan'."

msgid "Omega calculation with PFA failed."
msgstr "Perhitungan omega dengan PFA gagal."

msgid ""
"The analytic confidence interval is not available for coefficient omega "
"obtained with PFA. Change to 'Bootstrapped' in Advanced Options."
msgstr ""
"Interval kepercayaan analitis tidak tersedia untuk omega koefisien terambil "
"dengan PFA. Ubah ke 'Terbootstrap' di Opsi Lanjutan."

msgid "Omega interval calculation with PFA failed."
msgstr "Perhitungan interval omega dengan PFA gagal."

msgid ""
"The analytic confidence interval is not available for coefficient alpha/"
"lambda2 when data contain missings and pairwise complete observations are "
"used. Try changing to 'Delete listwise' within 'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"Interval kepercayaan analitis tidak tersedia untuk koefisien alfa/lambda2 "
"ketika data berisi observasi lengkap hilang dan berpasangan digunakan. Coba "
"mengubah ke 'Hapus berdaftar' dalam 'Opsi Lanjutan'."

msgid ""
"The analytic confidence interval is not available for the average interitem "
"correlation when data contain missings and pairwise complete observations "
"are used. Try changing to 'Delete listwise' within 'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"Interval kepercayaan analitis tidak tersedia untuk korelasi interitem rata-"
"rata ketika data berisi observasi lengkap hilang dan berpasangan digunakan. "
"Coba mengubah ke 'Hapus berdaftar' dalam 'Opsi Lanjutan'."

msgid "Omega item dropped statistics with CFA failed."
msgstr "Statistik item omega dihapus dengan CFA gagal."

msgid "Omega item dropped statistics with PFA failed."
msgstr "Statistik item omega dihapus dengan PFA gagal."

msgid ""
"The analytic confidence interval not available for coefficient alpha/lambda2 "
"when data contain missings and pairwise complete observations are used. Try "
"changing to 'Delete listwise' within 'Advanced Options'."
msgstr ""
"Interval kepercayaan analitis tidak tersedia untuk koefisien alfa/lambda2 "
"ketika data berisi observasi lengkap hilang dan berdaftar digunakan. Coba "
"mengubah ke 'Hapus berdaftar' dalam 'Opsi Lanjutan'."

msgid "Frequentist Scale Reliability Statistics"
msgstr "Statistik Keandalan Individu Frekuentis"

